        {
            "title": "中國對美國稀土磁鐵出口量10月達到九個月最高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d6mPomC4M2fAcCSqoIuejw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/af6ce2066c9a6d296c3698ae8ab3d127\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 上個月中國對美國的稀土磁鐵出口量達到1月以來的最高水平，上月雙方正在進行貿易談判，以穩定這種關鍵工業部件的供應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據周四公佈的中國海關數據，10月份中國對美國的稀土磁鐵出口量攀升至約656噸。這延續了5月份的反彈勢頭。當時由於北京實施了新的出口管制措施，導致5月中國對美國磁鐵出口量暴跌至不足50噸。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Eozv8UliPtLVkBXELsk1gQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/47f5ebfc77a3f6393cd97b27bafbc160\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從汽車到消費品再到武器，應用廣泛的稀土磁鐵成為中國在貿易戰中最有力的武器。中美雙方仍在商討北京如何放寬對美貿易限制——這是中國領導人習近平在10月底與川普會晤時達成的停火協議中做出的關鍵承諾，預計將在本月底達成協議。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e9b8a1d2-e35d-34e5-a830-0036fdf9579b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對美出口數據反映出，在經歷了最初的延誤和中斷之後，中國磁鐵出口全面復甦。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：中美兩國據悉仍在商討有關中國放寬稀土出口的關鍵細節</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Magnet Sales to US Reached Nine-Month High Before Truce</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
