        {
            "title": "債券交易員關注就業報告 攸關聯儲會降息的期待是幻滅或重燃",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/14TJ2pVatSgOHcwR3V6cbw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/83254978868741979f9f77ca82b2d092\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 債券投資者正密切關注周四的美國勞動力市場報告，該報告料將徹底澆熄或重新燃起市場對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>下個月降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受政府停擺影響而延遲發布的9月非農就業報告將於紐約時間8:30發布，這將是聯儲會決策者今年最後一次開會前發布的唯一官方主要就業數據。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一份顯示就業情況穩健的報告可能會削弱進一步降息的理由，並使規模達30萬億美元的美國國債市場進一步上漲的希望落空。另一方面，如果該報告的數據疲軟，則可能重燃市場對12月10日會議上連續第三次降息25個基點的預期，並提振本已有望創下2020年以來最佳年度表現的市場。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e8192f30-7e9c-3a00-9b46-b23d7661a215-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Fort Washington Investment Advisors的高級投資組合經理Dan Carter表示，鑑於對12月會議的定價，如果數據疲軟，市場反應會比數據符合預期或略高於預期的情況更大。在該會議召開前，聯儲會不會有太多一級數據公佈。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UmrXcW9Oo5C3FkfZ_FayHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/88fbe10269f2bf678e169ce29506c507\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近幾周來，市場對聯儲會12月降息的預期逐漸下降，一些政策制定者反對進一步寬鬆政策，通膨率繼續高於聯儲會2%的目標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至周三，市場對降息的機率估計約為35%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bond Traders Brace for Jobs Report as Fed Rate Cut Bets Crumble</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%94%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85%E6%98%AF%E5%B9%BB%E6%BB%85%E6%88%96%E9%87%8D%E7%87%83-033432581.html",
